undamentals/seo-starter-guide#check-if-google-can-see). *   [Organize your site](https://developers.google.com/search/docs/fundamentals/seo-starter-guide#organize). *   [Influence your title links](https://developers.google.com/search/docs/fundamentals/seo-starter-guide#titles). *   [Add images to your site, and optimize them](https://developers.google.com/search/docs/fundamentals/seo-starter-guide#images). *   [Next steps](https://developers.google.com/search/docs/fundamentals/seo-starter-guide#next-steps). Other sites linking to you is something that happens naturally over time, and you can also encourage people to discover your content by [promoting your site](https://developers.google.com/search/docs/fundamentals/seo-starter-guide#promoting). However this isn't required, and you should first focus on making sure [people know about your site](https://developers.google.com/search/docs/fundamentals/seo-starter-guide#promoting).\",\"score\":0.7016523,\"raw_content\":null},{\"url\":\"https://blueglassinsights.com/article/google-search-central-complete-guide-seo-documentation\",\"title\":\"The Complete Guide to Google's Official SEO Documentation\",\"content\":\"Google Search Central: The Complete Guide to Google's Official SEO Documentation. Whether you are a business owner trying to increase your organic traffic or a marketing director overseeing a complex website migration, understanding Google's official guidelines is your first step toward sustainable growth. In this comprehensive guide, we will walk you through the most critical sections of Google's resources. Formerly known as Google Webmaster Central, Google Search Central is the official hub for anyone who wants their content to be found on Google Search. It is a massive repository of tutorials, guidelines, best practices, and technical documentation designed to help website owners understand how Google views their sites. By aligning your website with what Google explicitly asks for, you remove friction from the crawling process and make it easier for search engines to reward your content. * **Bookmark the documentation:** Make the Google Search Central hub your first stop when you have a question about a specific SEO tactic or technical implementation.\",\"score\":0.6680367,\"raw_content\":null},{\"url\":\"https://www.searchenginejournal.com/googles-seo-starter-guide-set-for-a-major-update/506437\",\"title\":\"Google's SEO Starter Guide Set For A Major Update\",\"content\":\"Search Engine Journal - SEO, Search Marketing News and Tutorials. # Google’s SEO Starter Guide Set For A Major Update. * Google is updating its official SEO Starter Guide. * The guide will be more concise and focus on general concepts. * The revised guide will cut outdated advice and simplify SEO for beginners. Google is revamping its official SEO Starter Guide, streamlining advice for modern website owners, and simplifying complex topics. Google’s SEO Starter Guide, a critical resource for search engine optimization professionals, is undergoing a significant revision. First launched years ago, the SEO Starter Guide aims to explain the basics of improving website visibility in Google Search results. With over 8,000 words of advice, the current SEO Starter Guide remains one of the most visited resources on Google’s Search Central site. A key focus of the overhaul will be simplifying the content for modern users, especially those new to building websites.\",\"score\":0.6010557,\"raw_content\":null},{\"url\":\"https://keyword.com/blog/structured-data-seo-a-beginners-guide\",\"title\":\"Structured Data SEO: A Beginner’s Guide\",\"content\":\"So while Google’s coveted number one position on search queries isn’t a guarantee, you’d want to be as close to it as possible. Or at the very least, you want to be on the first page of Google search results. Today, we’re taking a look at structured data for SEO and how it can impact your website traffic and sales. ## What is Structured Data? Structured data refers to information that search engines like Google use to determine what a web page is all about. If a page contains information like a list of ingredients, measurements, and a set of instructions then Google will know that it’s looking at a recipe. Because it now knows the context behind a landing page’s content, it can deliver more relevant search results to its users. While this post will primarily focus on structured data, it’s worth noting that there are two other data types out there: semi-structured and unstructured data.\",\"score\":0.48425868,\"raw_content\":null},{\"url\":\"https://support.google.com/webmasters/thread/8982930/pdf-to-learn-seo?hl=en\",\"title\":\"PDF to learn SEO - Google Search Central Community\",\"content\":\"# PDF to learn SEO. Can google provide a complete SEO guide as pdf? I want to learn SEO from beginner to advanced level . I have the same question (12). Community content may not be verified or up-to-date.Learn more. Image 1 HugoMe Diamond Product Expert 💭 Let's see... The old Google SEO guidelines were in PDF format but the new guide is not anymore. You might checkhttps://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/7451184? Last edited Jun 30, 2019. 7/6/2019, 7:55:56 PM. https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/7451184. THis may help you perfectly or do more from google help. Google is BOSS than all I get help them. Image 3 ets Gold Product Expert. If you really want PDF format, you can still find the old guide on the Wayback Machine:. But it's _much better_ to use the latest guide if you can - on the link Hugo gave you. Send feedback about our Help Center. * Help Center* Community* Search Console. This help content & information General Help Center experience.\",\"score\":0.42591617,\"raw_content\":null}],\"response_time\":0.78,\"request_id\":\"b368470f-e92e-4c27-badf-fd46fac1da8b\"}"
